        <h2>Programs &amp; Services Guide</h2>
<p><a title="Open file in new window: StM-TownGuide-SS16-Web.pdf" href="/en/recreation-and-culture/Recreation-and-Culture-Town-Programs-and-Services-Guide.aspx?_mid_=99015" target="_blank"><img src="/en/resourcesGeneral/landing/fall-winter-guide-2016-2017-landing-page.png" alt="Programs and Services Guide cover" align="right"></a></p>
<p>The 2016/2017 Fall and Winter Programs and Services Guide is online! Pick up a print copy now at Town facilities.</p>
<p>Check out our recreation and culture programs as well as childcare and senior services.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a class="ContentButton" title="Open file in new window: StM-TownGuide-SS16-Web.pdf" href="/en/recreation-and-culture/Recreation-and-Culture-Town-Programs-and-Services-Guide.aspx?_mid_=99015" target="_blank">View Guide</a></p>
    
